      "date": "2017-10-25 06:34:14.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests uploaded by AT Release Candidate from trevis-71vm1 for review-dne-part-2 received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux 7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/c34e3b97-44e2-4395-adc8-999c41fe03ac). Ran 16 tests. No failures.",
